				<div id="post-10143" class="post-10143 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-economics tag-history tag-lifestyle-planning tag-patriotism">
					<h1 class="entry-title">Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/preppers-can-save-the-ideals-of-america" title="12:13 pm" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">August 6, 2013</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/preppers-can-save-the-ideals-of-america#comments" title="Comment on Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America">52 Comments</a></span>
											</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<div id="tweetbutton10143" class="tw_button" style="float:right;margin-left:10px;"><a href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fpreppers-can-save-the-ideals-of-america&amp;text=Episode-1180-%20How%20Preppers%20Can%20Save%20the%20Ideals%20of%20America&amp;related=&amp;lang=en&amp;count=horizontal&amp;counturl=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesurvivalpodcast.com%2Fpreppers-can-save-the-ideals-of-america" class="twitter-share-button"  style="width:55px;height:22px;background:transparent url('http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-tweet-button/tweetn.png') no-repeat  0 0;text-align:left;text-indent:-9999px;display:block;">Tweet</a></div><div class="podPress_content podPress_content_audio_mp3">
<div class="podpress_playerspace podpress_playerspace_audio_mp3 podpress_mp3player" style="display:block;" ><div id="podPressPlayerSpace_1"><!-- podPress --></div></div>
<div class="podPress_downloadlinks podPress_downloadlinks_audio_mp3"><a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2013/8-13/epi-01180-preparedness-and-the-ideals-of-america.mp3" target="new" title="Download: Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America" class="podpress_downloadimglink podpress_downloadimglink_audio_mp3"><img src="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/audio_mp3_button.png" class="podPress_imgicon podpress_imgicon_audio_mp3" alt="" /></a> <span class="podpress_mediafile_title podpress_mediafile_title_audio_mp3">Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America</span> <span class="podpress_mediafile_dursize podpress_mediafile_dursize_audio_mp3">[ 1:06:42 ]</span> <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_1" class="podpress_playlink podpress_playlink_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressShowHidePlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2013/8-13/epi-01180-preparedness-and-the-ideals-of-america.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;"><span id="podPressPlayerSpace_1_PlayLink" class="podPress_playerspace_playlink">Play Now</span></a><input type="hidden" id="podPressPlayerSpace_1_OrigURL" value="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2013/8-13/epi-01180-preparedness-and-the-ideals-of-america.mp3" /> | <a href="#podPressPlayerSpace_1" class="podpress_playinpopup podpress_playinpopup_audio_mp3" onclick="javascript:podPressPopupPlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2013/8-13/epi-01180-preparedness-and-the-ideals-of-america.mp3', 290, 24, 'The Survival Podcast', '10143', 'Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America', 'The Survival Podcast'); return false;">Play in Popup</a> | <a href="http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2013/8-13/epi-01180-preparedness-and-the-ideals-of-america.mp3" target="new" class="podpress_downloadlink podpress_downloadlink_audio_mp3">Download</a></div></div>
<script type="text/javascript">podPressShowHidePlayer('1', 'http://www.survivalpodcast.net/audio/2013/8-13/epi-01180-preparedness-and-the-ideals-of-america.mp3', 290, 24, 'false', 'http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/wp-content/plugins/podpress/images/vpreview_center.png', 'Episode-1180- How Preppers Can Save the Ideals of America', 'The Survival Podcast');</script><p>When people follow blind patriotism the worst deeds and ills of mankind become common place.  There is an old saying, &#8220;patriotism is the last refuge of a scoundrel&#8221; made famous by Samuel Johnson and today such patriotism is rampant.</p>
<p>War, poverty, fascism and more are all fine if you wrap it in the American flag.  So please don&#8217;t expect such flag waving drum beating in today&#8217;s show.  I don&#8217;t want to tell you what America is or even was but what it was promised to be.  I won&#8217;t lie to you and say that America will last forever, likely it won&#8217;t at least in its current form.</p>
<p>Yet there is an America that has tried to exist since she was founded, an America that lives up to the promises our founders made, and even they didn&#8217;t keep.  An America we can create if we choose to.  It is also possibly an America we might have to keep alive some day under another name.  We don&#8217;t know the future but we know that we alone are responsible to fulfill the promises of the past.</p>
<p><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Join Me Today As I Discuss&#8230;</span></strong></p>
<ul>
<li>How exactly are all men created equal and how are they not</li>
<li>What are natural rights and why must they be recognized for liberty to exist</li>
<li>What might the future of our nation hold, will we be here in 100 years</li>
<li>Why is the promise of America, only a promise</li>
<li>Why is it important to know our failures and our faults</li>
<li>Why only preparedness can fulfill the promise of America</li>
<li>Why we must believe that the promise is possible</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><span style="color: #800000;">Resources for Today’s Show…</span></strong></p>
